<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nigel-minns> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Nigel Minns became Regional Director for the East Midlands in March 2026. He was previously a Director of Children’s Services for 8 years and held a national role with the Association of Directors of Children’s Services. Nigel began his career as a primary school teacher and has also worked with the Office of the Regional Schools Commissioner as an external deputy director."@en .
